127
00:02:15,120 --> 00:02:18,160
[SPEAKER_02] Nikad nisu imali mogućnost, znate, osim da ih uznemiruju.

128
00:02:18,240 --> 00:02:20,480
[SPEAKER_02] I znate, ako želite uznemiravati rusku mornaricu, to je u redu.

129
00:02:20,720 --> 00:02:22,000
[SPEAKER_02] Rusi nemaju mnogo mornarice.

130
00:02:22,320 --> 00:02:24,160
[SPEAKER_02] To nije teško, zar ne?

131
